t":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"2 ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"flagship games, the first such endeavor between the two titles. As part of the collaboration, ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends 2","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" is featuring ‘Magical’ as the Word Of The Day on March 21, 2022.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"This press release features multimedia. View the full release here: ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20220321005379/en/","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20220321005379/en/","gated":false}],"gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"div","contentObject":[{"type":"img","src":"https://mms.businesswire.com/media/20220321005379/en/1395351/4/HPPS_WWF.jpg","alt":"(Graphic: Business Wire)","variations":[],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"(Graphic: Business Wire)","gated":false}],"gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\nBoth games have a strong connection to mischief. Magical Mischief is front and center in ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":", and ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"2","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" players often use mischievous strategy in gameplay, such as “besting” their opponent who just played a lengthy word by playing a much shorter word – including higher-scoring letters such as Z or X to get a more competitive score.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\nThe cross-game collaboration invites friendly mischief via in-game posts that encourage ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends 2","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" players to play a sneaky word and then pick a silly sticker to tease their opponent.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\nFrom March 21-28, 2022, players can participate in the cross-game Mischief With Friends sweepstakes that allow users to combine their love of word play with their magical puzzle skills while getting the chance to win amazing prizes, including exclusive merchandise. For details on sweepstakes entry and participation, players can visit ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fzynga.social%2FMischiefWithFriendsSweeps%26sa%3DD%26source%3Ddocs%26ust%3D1646181946152147%26usg%3DAOvVaw1BrAAnj5rZDDAEDVzfKe0F&esheet=52607017&newsitemid=20220321005379&lan=en-US&anchor=zynga.social%2FMischiefWithFriendsSweeps&index=2&md5=e509b9a02cd97eafc9422fe9e6569747","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"zynga.social/MischiefWithFriendsSweeps","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":".\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\nThe campaign also aligns with the ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells ","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"Mischief Season and the Magical Mischief event. Mischief Season runs from March 1-31, during which players can earn Points by completing various tasks in the game. By completing Puzzles during weeks in March when the Magical Mischief event is active, players will be able to send boxes that contain random Pranks to players in rival Clubs, either helping or hurting their progress in the spirit of friendly rivalry.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n“It’s a pleasure to connect the players of ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" and ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends 2","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":", two prominent titles that have captivated the hearts of our players while amassing a strong fan following over time,” said Yaron Leyvand, Executive Vice President, Games at Zynga. “This first-ever cross-collaboration between these titles allows players to experience fun synergies across their cherished games while enjoying playful, lighthearted mischief on their mobile devices.”\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\nLaunched in 2009, ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" has grown from popular mobile game to global pop culture sensation. Since then, the franchise has expanded to new platforms like Facebook Messenger, launched a hit sequel with ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Words With Friends 2","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" and brought innovative new ways to play to people around the world. The franchise’s success through this more than decade-long journey has been powered by player connections made through quick and clever wordplay that has become a touchstone in fans’ lives.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"typ