d":false},{"type":"text","content":", players enter a Match-3 adventure brimming with the spells, humour, colour and characters of the Harry Potter series. Featuring the soundtrack and voiceover recordings from the original Harry Potter films, fans follow an authentic, mobile retelling of Harry’s journey through the wizarding world. Earning spells and special boosts as they advance, players solve Match-3 puzzles populated with hopping Chocolate Frogs, fluttering Winged Keys, battling wizard chess pieces and other unexpected obstacles and objects. In the spirit of camaraderie and friendly competition at Hogwarts, players can join or form clubs with other fans to socialise, collaborate on puzzle strategies, share lives and vie for prizes in exclusive Club Events.\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" is playable on iOS and Android devices worldwide, as well as on Amazon Kindle and Facebook. For more information and to connect with other fans, follow us on ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHarryPotterPuzzlesAndSpells%2F&esheet=52607017&newsitemid=20220321005379&lan=en-US&anchor=Facebook&index=7&md5=13b6881d21bfa65b599aca4ecd37492a","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Facebook","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":", ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fharrypotterpuzzlesandspells%2F&esheet=52607017&newsitemid=20220321005379&lan=en-US&anchor=Instagram&index=8&md5=9ef4903a75ccb112ad84da728610303a","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Instagram","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" and ","gated":false},{"type":"a","href":"https://cts.busi